<br>
If you run into a situation where another raid makes it to phinny before your raid force is assembled than you should congratulate the other raid leader for getting assembled before you did and call your raid off and try to negotiate a drop or two for your friends.  This will save you and your friends much aggravation.  <br>
<br>
The phinney camp is a long haul for a wizard (14 times and around 2 months) and from your post it sounded like you were monopolizing the spawn (i.e. you killed phinney 12 hours before).  In my opinion you can't expect to win the competition for phinney every time and you know that you have lost the competition when another raid hits the kedge zone fully formed while you are still waiting for more people to show up.<br>
<br>
anyhoot my 2 bits<br>
