<br>
Anyway the same guild, came in in and started pulling, I tried to hail them, sent people tells, etc, to no use, to be honest  I did not think we we were ready, but I called for our puller to pull and off he went.  The next thing we know we have 4 sawhorses and phinnney on the ledge.  I had already targeted Phinney long  before he got there, and once he was there flux him, and started nuking. <br>
<br>
What it turned into was a huge train, I told my people to focus in Phinney, once the other guild realized this I had already been summoned 6 times, out to the 12 times I was summoned by phinney this go around.  I only had 9 people there, but just what I needed, since I don't have access to lvl 60 people.  All but 2 of my people were lvl 52, the the other two 57 and 59.  <br>
<br>
Anyway my group was 3 lvl 52s.  WE took the kill. And I actually killed Phinney.  I had my cleric camp with the train they pulled, and I was the main assist.  Yes I know I wizards should not tank.  <br>
<br>
Well my group of 3 took Phinney, yes there were 4 seahorses there, however we had not engaged them, the other group was still there.  As soon as they realized that phinney was dead, and they did not get the kill, they evaced and left us with thier train<br>
<br>
Well, I looted Phinney, dropped the BCS, amoung other drops, and called for an evac as I had already had our cleric camp, and knowing our druid was LOM after they left us with thier train<br>
<br>
Before I called for the evac, I had only lost one person to phinney ( the first person I have lost to him).  Now that they left us with thier train, my people did thier jobs, knowing I had laready had the cleric camp out, and continued to fight so the evacer in each group could evac. They both went down, but everyone else was evaced.<br>
<br>
Then Pia Fideles or whatever the hell they are called called fauled and petitioned that they were KS'ed.  All kind of threats came to me after from thier guild members.<br>
<br>
<br>
Two questions come to mind, more then that, I was the only person Phinney was summoning. I nuked him 15 times with Drought of Fire.  Now how does even with a wizard a group of 3 people, all lvl 52.  KS 12 people in 2 groups of 55  mostlly 60s?  And why would they petition sinceed they evaced out?<br>
<br>
<br>
Yes, I had to talk to the senior guide.  The issue is still open as far as I know till review of the logs.<br>
